      "abstract": unescape('Background%20When%20it%20was%20initiated%20in%202001%2c%20England%27s%20national%20patient%20survey%20programme%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20in%20the%20world%20and%20has%20now%20been%20widely%20emulated%20in%20other%20healthcare%20systems%2e%20The%20aim%20of%20the%20survey%20programme%20was%20to%20make%20the%20National%20Health%20Service%20%28NHS%29%20more%20%22patient%20centred%22%20and%20more%20responsive%20to%20patient%20feedback%2e%20The%20national%20inpatient%20survey%20has%20now%20been%20running%20in%20England%20annually%20since%202002%20gathering%20data%20from%20over%20600%2c000%20patients%2e%20The%20aim%20of%20this%20study%20is%20to%20investigate%20how%20the%20data%20have%20been%20used%20and%20to%20summarise%20what%20has%20been%20learned%20about%20patients%27%20evaluation%20of%20care%20as%20a%20result%2e%20Methods%20Two%20independent%20researchers%20systematically%20gathered%20all%20research%20that%20included%20analyses%20of%20the%20English%20national%20adult%20inpatient%20survey%20data%2e%20Journals%2c%20databases%20and%20relevant%20websites%20were%20searched%2e%20Publications%20prior%20to%202002%20were%20excluded%2e%20Articles%20were%20also%20identified%20following%20consultation%20with%20experts%2e%20All%20documents%20were%20then%20critically%20appraised%20by%20two%20co%2dauthors%20both%20of%20whom%20have%20a%20background%20in%20statistical%20analysis%2e%20Results%20We%20found%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20studies%20identified%20were%20reports%20produced%20by%20organisations%20contracted%20to%20gather%20the%20data%20or%20co%2dordinate%20the%20data%20collection%20and%20used%20mainly%20descriptive%20statistics%2e%20A%20few%20articles%20used%20the%20survey%20data%20for%20evidence%20based%20reporting%20or%20linked%20the%20survey%20to%20other%20healthcare%20data%2e%20The%20patient%27s%20socio%2ddemographic%20characteristics%20appeared%20to%20influence%20their%20evaluation%20of%20their%20care%20but%20characteristics%20of%20the%20workforce%20and%20the%2e%20At%20a%20national%20level%2c%20the%20results%20of%20the%20survey%20have%20been%20remarkably%20stable%20over%20time%2e%20Only%20in%20those%20areas%20where%20there%20have%20been%20co%2dordinated%20government%2dled%20campaigns%2c%20targets%20and%20incentives%2c%20have%20improvements%20been%20shown%2e%20The%20main%20findings%20of%20the%20review%20are%20that%20while%20the%20survey%20data%20have%20been%20used%20for%20different%20purposes%20they%20seem%20to%20have%20incited%20little%20academic%20interest%2e%20Conclusions%20The%20national%20inpatient%20survey%20has%20been%20a%20useful%20resource%20for%20many%20authors%20and%20organisations%20but%20the%20full%20potential%20inherent%20in%20this%20large%2c%20longitudinal%20publicly%20available%20dataset%20about%20patients%27%20experiences%20has%20not%20as%20yet%20been%20fully%20exploited%2e%20This%20review%20suggests%20that%20the%20presence%20of%20survey%20results%20alone%20is%20not%20enough%20to%20improve%20patients%27%20experiences%20and%20further%20research%20is%20required%20to%20understand%20whether%20and%20how%20the%20survey%20can%20be%20best%20used%20to%20improve%20standards%20of%20care%20in%20the%20NHS%2e'),
      "type": "article",
      "title": "The National Adult Inpatient Survey conducted in the English National Health Service from 2002 to 2009: how have the data been used and what do we know as a result?",
