      "abstract": unescape('Objectives%3a%20Previous%20research%20on%20nurse%20retention%20has%20focused%20mainly%20on%20its%20relationship%20with%20employment%20conditions%2e%20This%20study%20aimed%20to%20include%20an%20examination%20of%20the%20impact%20of%20nurses%27%20perceived%20barriers%20to%20delivering%20high%2dquality%20patient%2dcentred%20care%20on%20their%20intentions%20to%20leave%20their%20current%20employers%2e%20Methods%3a%20An%20American%20employee%20questionnaire%20was%20adapted%20for%20use%20with%20British%20nurses%2e%20The%20questionnaire%20was%20mailed%20to%206160%20nurses%20directly%20employed%20by%2020%20London%20hospitals%2e%20Up%20to%20two%20reminders%20were%20sent%20to%20non%2dresponders%2e%20The%20questionnaire%20asked%20nurses%20to%20report%20on%20experiences%20in%20their%20working%20lives%20and%20to%20state%20their%20intentions%20to%20leave%20or%20stay%20with%20their%20current%20employer%2e%20Demographic%20and%20employment%20history%20information%20was%20also%20elicited%2e%20Results%3a%20Responses%20were%20received%20from%202880%20%2847%25%29%2e%20Nurses%20report%20that%20the%20care%20they%20are%20able%20to%20provide%20often%20falls%20short%20of%20recognised%20standards%2e%20Factor%20analysis%20combined%2082%20questions%20on%20nurses%27%20experiences%20into%20four%20patient%2dcentred%20and%20four%20nurse%2dcentred%20dimensions%2e%20Nurses%20who%20report%20more%20problems%20in%20both%20nurse%2dcentred%20and%20patient%2dcentred%20dimensions%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20intend%20to%20leave%20their%20current%20employers%2e%20Satisfaction%20with%20pay%20and%20the%20cleanliness%20of%20work%20areas%20are%20also%20important%20factors%2e%20Conclusions%3a%20Standards%20of%20care%20are%20often%20perceived%20by%20nurses%20to%20be%20unacceptably%20poor%2e%20Furthermore%2c%20their%20experience%20of%20barriers%20to%20care%20has%20a%20demonstrable%20impact%20on%20their%20decision%20to%20leave%20or%20stay%20with%20their%20current%20employer%2e%20Nurse%20managers%20need%20to%20address%20the%20perceived%20barriers%20to%20providing%20high%2dquality%20care%20when%20considering%20nurse%20retention%20strategies%2e'),
